# 📝 Notes for Your Notebook

## Day 67 – AI Health Summary (UI)

### Topics Learned

* Using multiple cards to organize information.
* Displaying AI-generated explanations (currently sample text).
* Creating a health score section.
* Designing a report summary screen.

### Key Lesson

> **Medical values alone can be difficult for users to interpret. A summary written in simple language helps users understand what their results may mean. In future days, this summary will be generated dynamically using AI instead of fixed text.**

